<h1 id="nguá»“n-project-traditional-water-puppetry-games">[NGUá»’N Project: TRADITIONAL WATER PUPPETRY GAMES]</h1>

<p>Not only is water puppetry famous for the vibrant colors of the puppets but also for its attractive folk tales. Let NGUá»’N introduce you to some of the unique games of water puppetry (â€˜tÃ­ch trÃ²â€™ in Vietnamese)!</p>

<p>â€˜TÃ­châ€™ is understood as historical or literary legends that have been passed down through various generations. Combined with â€˜trÃ²â€™ representing the characters and images, stories (tÃ­ch) become more vivid than ever. Most water puppetry games (tÃ­ch trÃ²) depict the colorful cultural and working life of the people of the North Delta.</p>

<p>Tá»…uâ€™s joke
 Remembered for his image of a farmer who is poor yet honest, witty and spontaneous, Tá»…u is always the opening character for water puppet shows. NGUá»’N still remembers the joyful and bustling feeling whenever Tá»…u appears with his greetings and wishes for the audienceâ€™s health! Although he is always happy, he does not hesitate to attack corrupt officials and criticize the bad habits of the old social mandarins. Please take a look at NGUá»’Nâ€™s illustration to see if thereâ€™s anything special about this detail!</p>

<p>Buffalo grazing - Plowing - Rice milling
 The familiar image of industrious farmers plowing with buffalo in the middle of vast rice fields always mesmerizes NGUá»’N. Through the same name game (tÃ­ch trÃ²), we see the hard work of the farmers in the North as we feel the spirit of optimism in work. The image of a farmer turning tiring farming days into lively and joyful is always an inspiration for water puppetry as well as other arts.</p>

<p>Duck catching competition - Boat racing
 Who doesnâ€™t love festivals and village activities? NGUá»’N is no exception, always wanting to participate in exciting games every holiday. The bustling, vibrant and rich daily life of the people through these games is a worthy gift after moments of hard work. The puppets depicting strong men represent the abundant mental and physical health of people. This is not only a form of entertainment, but also a way to prepare yourself for good health and comfort!</p>

